                    <comment id="12689614" author="mikemccand" created="Thu, 26 Mar 2009 19:39:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch.  All tests pass, including a new one that showed the deadlock.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I also found &amp;amp; fixed a case where IndexWriter would hang during close (thinking a BG merge was still running when it wasn&apos;t) if the InterruptedException arrived at the right time.&lt;/p&gt;

